# Exception: a pre-seeded database (a real deterministic run of the mock agent's
# v1 and v2) is committed so the hosted dashboard shows the side-by-side
# regression on first load. On-boot seeding does not complete reliably on
# Streamlit Community Cloud, so the data ships in the repo instead.
